<br>
Not sure where Zerkers asking for shields is a viable answer. personally I don't really want the shield. I love dual wield. I like the concept of it. <br>
<br>
What would be a great thing to have from mythic is to determine how they separate Offensive vs Defensive output.<br>
<br>
As in DO they mean just your Armor and your ability to spec in certain lines and what natural abilities you have as a defensive output or do they mean just a portion of that... Hard to say.<br>
<br>
I think we can all agree on Offensive is basically your damage output. At least that's the way it seems to me. As in the only thing most care about is how hard you hit for.<br>
<br>
But then again Not sure if Mythic's reasoning for Merc/BM damage output to be so small when compared to a Zerker was because of there ability to have more defensive ouput. Who knows? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Either way it stands the light tanks simply do not meet their class description, i.e less offensive output then their realm's main tanks. I think that is our main point. Prior to this Patch yes Zerkers were meeting that description but the others were not. Now all 3 classes are in the toilet <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :( --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/frown.gif ALT=":("><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
As for defense. Not sure how Mythic ranks things... But i think Parry and Blocking is higher on the scale then evade 3? Not sure. That would be a NICE list to have... that way you could go through it and say ok he has this this and this.. check the chart each having a ranking take the avg and compare it to something else. kinda get what i mean?<br>
<br>
then again have studded armor which is viable to the most used type of damage in the game is a negative to defense... at least i would think so.<br>
<br>
Either way I thought zerkers were balance both ways. Can they toned down a bit... I can except 10-15 and raise other light tanks. I mean how long have we been asking for that?<br>
<br>
As it stands now if 1.62 goes live people will stop playing Zerkers and SBs... they will roll up savages or just not play. Warrior might become a bit more viable but people will see the damage output of a savage and roll that. I know I would.<br>
<br>
Oh the other thing I would love to comment on. People thing respecing a zerker to a 2H is a viable solution... it's not. If you want a 2H play a warrior or savage. they are WAY better suited for that then a zerker. I think it's a waste of time to respec something like 50 axe 50 parry or 50 axe 50 hammer. Your just going to gimp yourself more and if they every make any more changes to LA your be kicking yourself. The point of the class was to go dual weild... not 2H.<br>
<br>
